descp2: int, optional (default=None) - In a multiclass setting, specifies the class for which the PDPs should be computed. Note that for binary classification, the positive class (index 1) is always used. - In a multioutput setting, specifies the task for which the PDPs should be computed. Ignored in binary classification or classical regression settings.
